Assemble GitLab repository URL

Source: R/yay.gen.R
gl_url.Rd

Assemble GitLab repository URL

Usage

gl_url(
  id_proj,
  ...,
  ref = gl_branch_default(id_proj = id_proj, base_url = base_url, token = token,
    max_tries = max_tries),
  base_url = pal::pkg_config_val("gitlab_base_url"),
  token = pal::pkg_config_val("gitlab_token"),
  max_tries = 3L
)

Arguments

...

Optional path components added to the repository base URL.

Value

A character scalar.

See also

Other gitlabr: gl_file_raw(), gl_file_write()
